  • Throw on a cute hoodie the next time you're feeling cold

    The epitome of comfort meets cuteness! Step out in style and embrace the snug warmth of this charming hoodie, featuring two cute illustrated raccoons hugging each other.

    Crafted for both comfort and fashion, this Unisex Hoodie is a must-have for anyone who loves to flaunt their kawaii flair. Wear it out the next time you're friends, or at home when you need an extra layer.

    Available in 12 colors and 7 different sizes, Measurements are shown below. We recommend comparing the measurements to a hoodie that fits to avoid any disappointment. If in doubt, just go one size up because a larger hoodie is always comfy to wear!

  • Please follow the washing labels when cleaning the garment:

     Max temperature 30c, or cold water. Reverse garment to protect the print.

     Do not bleach

     Dry by the sun or hang it to dry. 

     Dry cleaning
